{"lastModified":1774607999290,"uri":"c::7580644256::vessel::d5cc7806-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Summer Operating Area: New England, USA\nWinter Operating Area: Bahamas & Florida, USA\n\nThis stunning and sleek Riva 90 Argo, BEYOND BEYOND is an eye-catching yacht offering both excellent performance and impressive volume. She is beautifully designed by Officina Italiana Design in partnership with the Ferretti Group. Ideal for a couple’s getaway or a family vacation she sleeps 6 guests in 4 staterooms. Her elegant interior is highlighted by full length side windows that open up onto the walk around deck on either side, allowing guests to embrace the ocean breeze. Forward of the dining table which seats eight, you will find the full beam owner’s suite, featuring a king size bed and comfortable lounge area. The ensuite features a double vanity and a spacious shower. The large windows throughout the suite offer natural light and a beautiful view. A full-beam VIP suite, 1 queen and 1 twin convertible to a queen are located on the lower deck, each with en-suite bathrooms. The social hub of the yacht is found on the flybridge where entertainment is key, featuring a wet bar, dining and lounging with a view of the stars through a retractable awning. Join our professional crew onboard and experience a trip that will take you BEYOND BEYOND your imagination.","blueprint":{"name":"BEYOND BEYOND","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7806-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c9TzQhQHGB.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7806-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4eaf62d0-edc2-11ef-9685-5dee05f78d5b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7806-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4e898b50-edc2-11ef-9684-5dee05f78d5b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7806-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4ecde750-edc2-11ef-9686-5dee05f78d5b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7806